HEADWORD: Speeder
<hw>Speed"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, speeds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Spinning)</fld> <def>A machine for drawing and
twisting slivers to form rovings.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Speedful</ent>⟦br⟧
